  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d195b4b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlFbkCdypR1qYerHhTSPT4tVnMw7AVTibL9pjdJxUz49oqBotFHQO28Txx37Fo4vTiaVuhLjWbtA343g%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>有一个场景，Claude Code的能力是无可比拟的——对需求！</p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.85 !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.85 !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">刚才有位朋友问我：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">「你不是早就切换到Codex了吗，怎么Claude Code用量还是这么大？」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.85 !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我的回答是：</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 28px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:20px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:17px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;list-style-type:decimal;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 2px 6px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 700;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">每个模型都有自己独特的优势</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">、都有对应适合场景，没有什么模型包打天下。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 2px 6px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 700;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有一个场景，Claude Code的能力是无可比拟的——对需求！</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.85 !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为什么？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.85 !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">得益于以下四点：</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 28px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:20px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:17px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;list-style-type:decimal;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Claude Opus 4.5是目前综合能力Top 3的编程模型</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它的速度比另外两个Top模型更</span></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 2px 6px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 700;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">快</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Claude系列模型很擅长</span></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 2px 6px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 700;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">说人话</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，它使用的语言不像Codex系列模型那样不好理解。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Claude Code有一个独特的</span></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 2px 6px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 700;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AskUserQuestion</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的交互，其他编程Agent暂时还没抄走。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.85 !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">因此，Claude Code非常适合对需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.85 !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;text-decoration: underline;\">“等等，小排哥，前三点你都讲过了，第四点「AskUserQuestion」是个什么玩意？”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0px !important;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 1.85 !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">来了！马上讲。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AskUserQuestion是Claude Code自带的一个小工具。它其实会被自动触发。如果你没有见过它，你也可以显式强调你要这个工具。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">假如我们要做一个“与众不同的贪吃蛇游戏”，你可以尝试在Claude Code里输入这段。</span></span></p>\n  <pre><code><pre style=\"border-radius:6px;padding:0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;\"><code style=\"padding:16px 20px;white-space:pre-wrap;display:block;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;line-height:1.7;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我要做一个不同寻常的贪吃蛇游戏。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">使用AskUserQuestion工具，像苏格拉底一样帮助我完善需求。</span></span></code><br></pre></code><br></pre>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">然后你就会看到这样的界面，Claude Code会调用AskUserQuestion，弹出来选择题，让你做。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这样的对需求过程，非常惬意。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5185185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 500px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100016875\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c81b89ff&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFbkCdypR1qYerHhTSPT4tVrSEhG2nljfc